ound? Friction. Friction is very low because they slide they slide almost without any, you know, without, losing any any power. So so they they speeding up very fast, and and this is great. I mean, the the it looks like very easy, but it is not easy at all. Yeah. Yeah. It is on on the frozen lake on on the snow. And the difference is that if if you''re doing cat surfing just regular on water, you''re losing a lot of power because water is is not sliding. And it it water is stops you all the time, and you have to generate, like, negative power on on the on the water to to balance the the power on on in the kite. Right? So so so we''re losing a lot of power doing this. If you have ski, you have you have the edge of the ski, and it is very little. So you you you you''re losing", "confidence": 0.99316406, "words": [{"word": "i''m", "start": 5.7599998, "end": 6.16, "confidence": 0.9970703, "punctuated_word": "I''m"}, {"word": "very", "start": 6.16, "end": 6.3999996, "confidence": 0.99902344, "punctuated_word": "very"}, {"word": "well", "start": 6.3999996, "end": 6.72, "confidence": 0.9995117, "punctuated_word": "well."}, {"word": "how", "start": 6.72, "end": 6.96, "confidence": 1, "punctuated_word": "How"}, {"word": "are", "start": 6.96, "end": 7.12, "confidence": 0.9892578, "punctuated_word": "are"}, {"word": "you", "start": 7.12, "end": 7.3599997, "confidence": 1, "punctuated_word": "you?"}, {"word": "you''re", "start": 13.245, "end": 13.725, "confidence": 0.97387695, "punctuated_word": "You''re"}, {"word": "doing", "start": 13.725, "end": 13.965, "confidence": 1, "punctuated_word": "doing"}, {"word": "very", "start": 13.965, "end": 14.285, "confidence": 1, "punctuated_word": "very"}, {"word": "well", "start": 14.285, "end": 14.525, "confidence": 1, "punctuated_word": "well"}, {"word": "in", "start": 14.525, "end": 14.684999, "confidence": 1, "punctuated_word": "in"}, {"word": "warm", "start": 14.684999, "end": 15.485, "confidence": 0.39575195, "punctuated_word": "warm